  <brief_title>Full-thickness Skin vs. Synthetic Mesh in the Repair of Large Incisional Hernia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Full-thickness Skin vs. Synthetic Mesh in the Repair of Large Incisional Hernia - a Prospective Randomized Controlled Study</official_title>
