  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective randomized study to compare surgical methods for the repair of large
      abdominal hernia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with giant (&gt;10 cm in diameter) abdominal wall hernia are included in a prospective
      randomized study comparing conventional mesh repair with the best possible method to onlay
      full thickness skin grafts.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
