  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Rate of complication</measure>
    <time_frame>3 month, 1 year and 3 year post-operative clinical follow-up</time_frame>
    <description>Complications will be assessed over a 3 year period of regular follow-up by an objective surgeon who is unaware of which surgical method which was used. Eventual complications may include infection, bleeding, seroma and fistula formation.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
